com.github.dandelion.datatables.core.extension

Interface Extension

  • All Known Implementing Classes:
    AbstractExtension, AbstractFilteringFeature, AjaxFeature, AjaxReloadFeature, AppearFeature, Bootstrap2Theme, Bootstrap3Theme, ColReorderPlugin, ExportFeature, ExternalFilterFeature, ExtraHtmlFeature, ExtraJsFeature, FilteringFeature, FilteringFeature, FixedHeaderPlugin, JQueryUITheme, PagingTypeBootstrapFullFeature, PagingTypeBootstrapFullNumbersFeature, PagingTypeBootstrapSimpleFeature, PagingTypeExtJsFeature, PagingTypeInputFeature, PagingTypeListboxFeature, PagingTypeScrollingFeature, PipeliningFeature, ResponsivePlugin, ScrollerPlugin, ServerSideFeature, SortingFeature

    public interface Extension

    Common interface for all extensions. An extension can be a plugin (e.g. ScrollerPlugin, ColReorderPlugin), a feature (e.g. PagingTypeBootstrapSimpleFeature, AbstractFilteringFeature add-on) or a theme (e.g. Bootstrap2Theme).

    An extension can be composed of :

    • one or more JsResource, i.e. Javascript code externalized in a file
    • one or more CssResource, i.e. CSS code externalized in a file
    • one or more Parameter, i.e. one or more specific DataTables parameters that will be used during the DataTables initialization
    • afterAll
    TODO These attributes can be visualized in the following Javascript snippet :
